paper_metadata.title: MAIN TEXT
paper_metadata.extraction_summary: The paper discusses a high-throughput screening assay for identifying drugs that improve membrane expression of trafficking-deficient KV11.1 (KCNH2) variants. No specific KCNH2 genetic variants with penetrance data were reported.

challenges: The paper did not provide specific genetic variant data for KCNH2, focusing instead on assay development.
extraction_metadata.notes: The paper primarily focuses on the development of a high-throughput assay and does not provide detailed genetic variant information or penetrance data for KCNH2.
